DIS weer sulke tyd. Die 90ste Oscars word op 4 Maart weer deur Jimmy Kimmel aangebied. Dié jaar is die glansaand darem nie weer so spierwit nie. Hier is so ’n voorsmakie van sommige benoemings wat dié week aangekondig is. Op die lys vir beste fliek is daar Call Me By Your Name, Darkest Hour, Dunkirk, Get Out, Lady Bird, Phantom Thread, The Post, The Shape of Water en Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri. As beste manlike hoofspeler: Timothée Chalamet (Call Me By Your Name), Daniel Day-Lewis (Phantom Thread), Daniel Kaluuya (Get Out), Gary Oldman (Darkest Hour), en Denzel Washington (Roman J. Is­rael Esq). Die leading ladies: Sally Hawkins (The Shape of Water), Francis McDormand (Three Billboards outside Ebbing, Missouri), Margot Robbie (I, Tonya), Saoirse Ronan (Lady Bird) en natuurlik Meryl Streep (The Post).